{
  "stem": "16473.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] I don't remember anything being told to me other than that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a point in time when my mother sent me away to a-- a border town between Hungary and Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- I-- I definitely had the feeling that it was unsafe to be in, in, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what was in Hungary, in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I-- I was prepped to go there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I-- I was taught the Catholic prayer, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] some other things about, you know, being a Christian so that I could pass as a Christian.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was sent to live with-- with some peasants in-- in this, in this border town.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I don't remember anybody explaining to me why this is happening except that it's dangerous to be here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went there on a train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Probably with my mother, probably my mother took me there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm not-- I don't recall that, because I remember coming back, and I came back by myself, and she met me at the train station.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I might have been just put on the train and then received there by these people, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably not.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Probably this is the time he was in work camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is probably how I found out it was dangerous because at one point my dad was packing his-- his things and he was crying.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you know, there was a big to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he-- he was sent to work camp and we didn't know if we'd see him again or not.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So was a-- you know, as a child, I must have perceived that this was a very, you know, threatening situation.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
